{"tid":360521,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【聖徒改姓高】修咸頓21億易主 英超第二隊變中資","createTime":"2017-08-15T10:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T06:24:10.000Z","uid":25125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b65cbbb92a683aa68a4e80c73678c7f1817a0b8","tid":360521,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:57:55.000Z","msg":"【聖徒改姓高】修咸頓21億易主<br />\n英超第二隊變中資<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170814/large/1502723614_0b08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170814%2Flarge%2F1502723614_0b08.jpg&h=31fbb04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高繼勝及其家族成為修咸頓大股東<br />\n<br />\n又一中資財團入主英超！一直想賣盤的修咸頓班主賴貝靴爾（Katharina Liebherr），周一宣佈與64歲的中國商人高繼勝及其家族達成協議，高氏將成為修咸頓大股東。雖然球會未有透露賣出的股份比例及價錢等資料，不過據報高繼勝以2.1億鎊（約21億港元）收購「聖徒」的80%股份，而現有的董事會成員暫時不會有變動。<br />\n<br />\n賴貝靴爾在致球迷的公開信表示：「高繼勝先生、他的女兒Nelly Gao和我都非常信任現時的管理團隊，我們將建立可持續發展的合作模式。」至於高繼勝亦有簡短公開信與球迷打招呼：「我們希望在未來幾年取得更長足的進步，期待球會進入下一個精彩篇章。」<br />\n高繼勝是萊茵達體育發展股份有限公司的董事長，該公司於1988年在杭州成立，2002年步入地產商行列，近年發展體育產業。高繼勝本人據報更曾當兵、下鄉務農、做記者、武警、甚至寫散文。<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20170815/57081584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20170815%2F57081584&d=CcDQHTJkwWMWMHuO2eWxe8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=218bfc44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20170815%2F57081584&h=8e8cff3d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20170815/57081584</a>"},{"pid":"c82e5db877a572766658e6402f75bc2881b28ec0","tid":360521,"uid":136116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:05:36.000Z","msg":"利記二隊到時有錢到買返利記一隊啲人就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97692c49ec5099ef4d102f40cfd3c5f541e35c90","tid":360521,"uid":23190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:10:30.000Z","msg":"又武警又記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8dfa3e788cf6d14638d1cf77cf9198b5a39bb7","tid":360521,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"第一支係屈記定？？？"},{"pid":"7e9a151e6a5b31dd5fbbd56c8389d30e1df39250","tid":360521,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:49:26.000Z","msg":"平過尼馬"},{"pid":"6db78bb749c8faa989ee5674ecf43e3f5713f97f","tid":360521,"uid":78122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一支係屈記定？？？</blockquote><br />\n伯明翰？"},{"pid":"f135f5ab755341f8bf7267027daaf753ccd66b63","tid":360521,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平過尼馬</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab029ec3be4ca9fe7f1520d40393fde56868c993","tid":360521,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:54:52.000Z","msg":"要啦 0:0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf49c06d9d058500af66d103af8650e5cb6dba7","tid":360521,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T14:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平過尼馬</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好抵